data.description: Welcome to 1145 Wade Street where you're getting two properties in one. As you enter the property you will be greeted by the open floor plan in the main living room and the newly renovated kitchen ahead. To the right side hallway are the two bedrooms and shared bathroom. This property features a new 520 sq ft studio style Carriage House/Additional Dwelling Unit in addition to the main home. This is the perfect property for a dual income investment opportunity or living in one unit and renting the other! The Carriage House features a bathroom with a tiled shower, loft that will fit a king size bed, a full kitchen, large inviting windows, and a sliding glass door. The main house has been renovated as well with an added half bathroom and remodeled kitchen opening up the floor plan. The kitchen features new granite countertops, new tile flooring, and new appliances. There is also a new tankless water heater. Original hardwood floors flow throughout the main floor and bedrooms.
